// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0732 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3d5be9b2-c42c-5ce5-9d94-70ce5cadcdb5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
